{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8cd6a1ea11","title":"上海市管制反革命分子暂行办法","origin":"根据文件的原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"845758990e","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":2,"articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2368652596","type":"title","text":"上海市管制反革命分子暂行办法","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"04c9063c12","type":"subtitle","text":"(上海市军事管制委员会一九五一年七月二日公布)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"54393e7574","type":"paragraph","text":"第一条  为巩固人民民主专政，维护人民民主事业，巩固革命秩序，根据共同纲领第七条及惩治反革命条例之精神，并贯彻镇压与宽大相结合的方针，参酌本市具体情况，特制定本办法。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"63bc92662b","type":"paragraph","text":"第二条  对反革命分子之法律制裁，除死刑徒刑外，其罪行较轻而不足判处徒刑者，得衡情处以一年至五年之管制。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"529eff379b","type":"paragraph","text":"第三条  凡经下列各机关所决定管制之反革命分子，均由执行管制机关予以管制：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"1cd3f7c924","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）上海市军事管制委员会决定者；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"ba817c1e24","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）上海市人民法院判决者；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"04b37452ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）上海市人民法庭判决者；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"39e67c7bca","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）淞沪警备司令部军法处判决者；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"2395fa4965","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）外地各军事或司法机关判决而经批准旅沪或迁沪者。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"c0ed37dc04","type":"paragraph","text":"第四条  管制反革命分子之执行机关为上海市人民政府公安局。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"6c67e6d308","type":"paragraph","text":"第五条  对反革命分子之管制，除由公安机关管制外，当地人民团体或人民群众有监督及检举其不法言行之权利。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"acab090b25","type":"paragraph","text":"第六条  凡被管制之反革命分子，在管制期间，应剥夺其下列权利之一部或全部：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"62bf5e84a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）选举权与被选举权；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"c29372d6d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）担任国家职务之权；","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"d97aa4f777","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）担任公共团体职务之权；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"b7eb5cf863","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）受国家勋章奖章及荣誉称号之权；","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"60cf2eec97","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）受领恤金之权利；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"06b43b3e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）言论、著作、出版、结社、集会、旅行、迁徙等自由；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"80cdea565c","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）特种职业权及特种营业权。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"da3ea7db19","type":"paragraph","text":"第七条  受管制之反革命分子必须切实遵守：","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"18d543e6c1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）人民政府之各种法律法令政策布告，及执行管制机关之一切决定与命令；","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"d1e815f175","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）积极参加劳动生产，从事正当职业；","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"1dcc14a2e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）接受当地人民团体或人民群众之监督。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"3eb757b43f","type":"paragraph","text":"第八条  执行管制机关，认为必要时，得指定受管制者于一定地区，一定职业范围内，予以劳动改造或思想教育。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"58cad1a3e7","type":"paragraph","text":"第九条  受管制之反革命分子，如违犯管制规则，或继续有从事反革命行为者，得由执行管制机关提请有关机关，作下列之处理：","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"a42c472589","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）剥夺其未被剥夺之权利（如仅部分被剥夺权利者）；","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"2c67e4531c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）延长其全部或一部之管制期限；","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"2f88467a43","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）依法惩办。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"f79ea95ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"第十条  执行管制机关，除按照判决进行管制外，遇有下列情况，得提请原判决机关予以酌情缩短管制期限或解除管制：","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"2d1637b491","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）受管制者于管制期内切实遵守人民政府各项法令，积极改造自己，真诚悔改确有表现，有当地群众或群众团体证明，并经执行管制机关审查认可者；","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"ddf21853aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）受管制者于管制期内努力改造自己，并为人民立功有显著成绩，且有政府机关之证明，而经执行管制机关审查认可者。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"ff5f34c14b","type":"paragraph","text":"受管制者于管制期内，虽改造已有成效，但不足缩短或解除其管制期限时，得先行部分解除其已被剥夺的某一种或数种权利。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"88cb3bdc61","type":"paragraph","text":"第十一条  本办法在中央或华东管制条例公布后，即按中央或华东公布之条例予以修正或废止之。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"},{"id":"5d6f9d9410","type":"paragraph","text":"第十二条  本办法自公布之日起施行。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11"}],"page":{"id":"ef51344947","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8cd6a1ea11","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}